13 inspected. This subsection shall not apply to a food establishment whose
14 primary function is not in connection with any premises licensed,
15 registered or permitted pursuant to the respective law or rule and
16 regulation of such secretary.
17 Sec. 3. K.S.A. 65-689 is hereby repealed.
18 Sec. 4. This act shall take effect and be in force from and after its
19 publication in the statute book.

